# Drizzle Kit output (SQL migrations, snapshots) — not tracked in git.
# Run `pnpm exec drizzle-kit generate` locally when needed; do not commit generated files.
#
# `_journal.json` is committed empty so `drizzle-kit migrate` / `generate` never hit ENOENT on a fresh clone
# (Kit reads meta/_journal.json before creating it). Regenerated migrations still stay ignored via `*`.
*
!.gitignore
!meta/_journal.json
